# Implementation Plan - Handover Report Refinements

This plan focuses on improving the contrast and spacing of the "Handover Report Details" section to ensure high readability and a professional, non-synthetic appearance.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Contrast**: I will change all 'Handover' labels and text to pure black/near-black.
> - **Aesthetics**: I will replace the thick vertical accent bars with a more standard "boxed container" style (subtle borders) to move away from the overly stylized layout.
> - **Spacing**: Padding inside the handover blocks will be increased to improve "breathability".

